[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0585","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0585.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0353","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9107,\"outputTokens\":28,\"totalTokens\":10799}}","description":"HP-UX 系统中的 rpc.pcnfsd 服务存在权限配置错误漏洞，远程未经身份认证的攻击者可通过修改主打印机假脱机目录的权限，获取远程 root 权限访问。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过篡改打印机假脱机目录权限实现权限提升至 root 权限，严重威胁系统安全。建议升级至修复版本或禁用 rpc.pcnfsd 服务。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0353"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.860","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 到最新的Patched-Up 11.11 或更高版本，并应用最新的安全补丁包。具体步骤：1. 执行\"swinstall -s /somepath/hpus11v1_patch\"安装补丁；2. 检查并删除不必要的rpc.pcnfsd服务，使其处于禁用状态；3. 在防火墙上配置规则，仅允许本地网络段访问rpc.pcnfsd端口；4. 验证/spool目录的权限，确保持有者为root且权限为755，禁止其他用户修改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-026.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9902-091","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0353","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0353.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2cv7-m7r7-5xxj/GHSA-2cv7-m7r7-5xxj.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/h/hpux_PHCO_14625.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/hpux_PHKL_15689.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x6000/5377/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0585.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0610","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0610.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0370","title":"Sun Solaris 与 SunOS man 及 catman 任意文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 和 SunOS 系统中的 man 与 catman 命令存在文件覆盖漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用这些命令在处理临时文件时的缺陷，将任意文件写入目标系统上的指定路径，实现文件覆盖或权限提升。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 及 SunOS 多个版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限。厂商已发布相应安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0370"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.047","remediation":"建议升级到 Sun 官方补丁对应的 Solaris 版本（如 Solaris 2.6 及更新版本已修复此问题），或从 sunsolve.sun.com 获取 man/catman 相关安全补丁。临时缓解措施：以 root 权限执行 `chmod 755 /usr/bin/man /usr/bin/catman` 移除 setuid 位，防止普通用户利用提权覆盖任意文件。同时通过 `tty` 访问控制限制本地用户登录高危账户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/165"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0610.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0603","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0603.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0367","title":"NetBSD netstat 本地内核内存访问漏洞","description":"NetBSD 系统的 netstat 命令存在本地内核内存泄露漏洞。由于 netstat 工具在处理网络统计信息时未能正确限制对内核内存区域的访问权限，本地攻击者可通过执行特制的 netstat 命令读取内核敏感数据，导致内核信息泄露。该漏洞影响早期 NetBSD 版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限才能利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0367"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.657","remediation":"升级 NetBSD 至 1.4.1 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 NetBSD 1.4.1 的安全补丁中修复。如无法升级，可通过 chmod 700 /usr/bin/netstat 限制 netstat 命令的执行权限，仅允许 root 用户使用，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7571"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0603.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0604","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0604.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0368","title":"WU-FTPD ProFTPD realpath 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"WU-FTPD 2.4.2、SCO Open Server 5.0.5 及 ProFTPd 1.2 pre1 等 FTP 服务器软件中的 realpath 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务发送特制的路径请求触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用此漏洞可在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现完全控制服务器。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，且已有公开利用代码。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0368"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.780","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.6.2 及以上版本，或升级 ProFTPd 至 1.2.1 及以上版本。SCO Open Server 用户应安装最新补丁包或迁移至受支持的操作系统。如无法升级，在 inetd 配置中禁用 FTP 服务或使用 TCP Wrappers 限制访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0368","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19087","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7638326ff3f30ccdb52a67547408dd61f5cdc6cc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0368.json","https://github.com/REMath/implementations/blob/045b59dc77d5bd3e9a14713898ebcfdebacd11e9/tanalysis/tanalysis/verisec%20v1.0/wu-ftpd/CVE-1999-0368/README","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0368","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0368.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0368.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pjq9-4mrj-pv4g/GHSA-pjq9-4mrj-pv4g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/westtide/open-source-case-studies/blob/57e71842cdb3e034316b0d083f8d19f680501b67/verisec/.frama-c/programs_apps_wu-ftpd_CVE-1999-0368_realpath-linkpath_prefix_ok.eva/nonterm.log","https://github.com/tomhart-msc/verisec/blob/02f3a9660885181705e7550b8609534bbbaa414c/programs/apps/wu-ftpd/CVE-1999-0368/README","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0368.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0604.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0648","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0648.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0407","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 /IISADMPWD 虚拟目录暴力破解密码代理漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 默认安装包含 /IISADMPWD 虚拟目录，该目录中的文件可被攻击者用作暴力破解密码攻击的代理，或用于识别系统中的有效用户账户，导致敏感信息泄露和未授权访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0407"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1999-02-09","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"删除 /IISADMPWD 虚拟目录或限制其访问权限；升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本并使用最新 IIS。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T14:05:38.472358263+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91983486431506&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92000623021036&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0648.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0578","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0578.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0350","title":"Rational Software ClearCase for Unix db_loader 条件竞争本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM Rational ClearCase for Unix 3.2 版本中的 db_loader 程序存在竞态条件漏洞。本地攻击者利用该程序在处理 SUID 位设置时的时序问题，通过精心构造的竞争条件操作，可在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。攻击者需要具备本地系统访问权限，且成功利用需满足特定的时序窗口条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0350"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-08","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 IBM Rational ClearCase 的修复版本（3.2 之后的版本已修复此问题）。由于该产品已停止维护，建议迁移到受支持的配置管理解决方案，或在系统层面限制不可信用户对 db_loader 程序的执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0350","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0350"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0578.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0601","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0601.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0366","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 网络共享空密码认证绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 存在空密码认证绕过漏洞。由于系统在处理空 NT 哈希值时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过使用空密码直接访问目标系统的网络共享资源，无需提供有效凭据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者利用此漏洞可获取共享文件及敏感数据的读取权限，危害程度较高。Microsoft 已在安全公告 MS99-004 中发布修复更新。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0366"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-08","updated":"1999-02-08","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-004 提供的修补程序（对应 KB 文章 Q214840），该补丁修正了 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 中 SAM 认证逻辑错误。如无法安装补丁，可禁用域控制器上来自 DOS/Windows 3.1/Windows for Workgroups/OS/2/Macintosh 客户端的密码更改功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0366.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0366","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0366.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0366.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5fcq-r7m3-pxf5/GHSA-5fcq-r7m3-pxf5.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0366.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e0b64613-6d45-4a3b-8434-c9c2ceedf571.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000517.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0601.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0599","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0599.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0365","title":"Metamail mailcap 条目未过滤 shell 元字符远程命令执行漏洞","description":"metamail 邮件处理工具包中存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞，在将邮件内容传递给 mailcap 条目处理时未对 shell 元字符进行正确引号转义，导致远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制邮件触发命令执行。攻击者利用该漏洞可在受害者系统上以当前用户权限执行任意命令，影响广泛部署 metamail 的 Unix/Linux 系统。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0365"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.403","remediation":"升级 metamail 至 2.7-9 或更高版本，该版本已对 mailcap 文件中的 shell 元字符进行正确转义处理。如无法升级，可临时移除或禁用系统中所有不可信来源的 mailcap 配置项，同时限制邮件客户端自动调用 metamail 处理附件。在 sendmail 环境下，建议禁用自动执行 mailcap 条目的功能，并审查 /etc/mailcap 及用户 ~/.mailcap 中的每条规则，确保不含未引用的 shell 元字符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0365","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0365","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0365.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gmgp-r787-3hjp/GHSA-gmgp-r787-3hjp.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000513.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0365.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0599.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0594","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0594.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0362","title":"Ipswitch WS_FTP Server 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ipswitch WS_FTP Server 1.0.1 及 1.0.2 版本存在远程拒绝服务漏洞。未经身份认证的攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的 CWD（Change Working Directory）命令，导致 FTP 服务进程异常崩溃或停止响应，从而中断正常的文件传输服务。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危，受影响用户应升级至更高版本以修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0362"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.990","remediation":"升级至 WS_FTP Server 1.0.3 及以上版本可修复此漏洞；在防火墙中限制 FTP 服务端口的访问来源 IP，防止未授权远程连接发起 CWD 命令攻击。鉴于该产品版本过于老旧，建议迁移至受支持的最新版 WS_FTP Server 或替代 FTP 服务软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD02021999.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/217","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0362","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0362.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/wsftp_cwd_dos.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/Ipswitch%20WS_FTP%20Server%20prior%205.0.2%20CWD%20path%20denial%20of%20service.plugin","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0594.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0619","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0619.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0383","title":"ACC Tigris 未授权访问漏洞","description":"ACC Tigris 存在未授权访问漏洞，远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可直接访问系统管理界面，获取敏感信息或执行未授权操作。该漏洞影响 ACC Tigris 产品，攻击者只需网络可达即可利用，无需复杂攻击条件。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0383"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.773","remediation":"ACC Tigris 产品已停止维护，无官方补丁可用。建议立即在 Web 服务器前端部署反向代理（如 Nginx/Apache）并配置 HTTP 基本认证或 IP 白名单访问控制；同时在网络防火墙层面限制对 ACC Tigris 服务端口（默认 80）的访问来源，仅允许受信 IP 段连接。长期方案为迁移至受支持的现代 Web 服务器软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/267","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/183","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0383.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0383","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0383.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0383.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7hmx-xxrr-h2wg/GHSA-7hmx-xxrr-h2wg.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/account_public_public.nasl","https://github.com/LubyRuffy/plugins/blob/f873b19f27c95eaf2993ca4acde5cb7965d2ee3f/pre2008/acc.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0383.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0619.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0619.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0595","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0595.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0363","title":"SuSE Linux 5.2 lpc 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"S.u.S.E Linux 5.2 系统中的 lpc 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 lpc 程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 S.u.S.E Linux 5.2 版本，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0363"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-02","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 SuSE Linux 至 5.3 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。临时缓解措施：移除 lpc 程序的 setuid 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/lpc），限制本地普通用户执行该程序。如非必要，可停止并禁用 lpd 打印服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/328","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19259"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0595.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0595.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0595.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0485","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0485.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0291","title":"Qbik WinGate 代理默认无密码未授权访问漏洞","description":"WinGate 代理服务器在默认安装时未设置访问密码，导致缺乏必要的身份认证机制。远程攻击者可在无需任何认证的条件下连接至该代理服务，利用其开放的代理功能转发网络连接请求，从而隐藏攻击来源、绕过访问控制或发起匿名攻击。该漏洞影响 WinGate 全系列早期版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0291"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.093","remediation":"立即为 WinGate 代理服务设置管理密码并启用用户认证机制；在 GateKeeper 管理控制台中配置访问控制列表，仅允许受信任的内部 IP 地址段使用代理服务；如业务不需要代理功能，直接卸载或禁用 WinGate 服务；同时在网络防火墙层面拦截外部对 8080/1080 等常见代理端口的入站连接作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0291","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0291.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0291","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0291.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/wingate.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0485.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0583","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0583.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0351","title":"多厂商 FTP 服务器 PASV 模式拒绝服务与未授权数据访问漏洞","description":"FTP 协议 PASV 被动模式存在设计缺陷，远程攻击者可利用竞争条件在合法客户端之前连接至服务器为该客户端开放的临时数据端口，导致未经授权的数据访问和敏感信息窃取。若攻击者抢先占用该数据端口，还可导致合法客户端无法完成数据传输，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多种 FTP 服务器实现，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0351"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.610","remediation":"升级至支持 PASV 地址绑定检查的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd 3.0+、ProFTPD 1.3.5+），配置数据端口仅接受与控制连接相同 IP 的连接请求。启用 FTPS（FTP over TLS/SSL，RFC 2228）加密数据通道防止窃听；条件允许时切换到 SFTP/SCP。在服务器上限制 PASV 端口范围为固定区间，并通过防火墙仅允许预期客户端 IP 访问该端口段作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://attrition.org/security/advisory/misc/infowar/iw_sec_01.txt","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3389","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0351","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0351.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8xwf-5pv7-g2w4/GHSA-8xwf-5pv7-g2w4.json","https://github.com/CWE-CAPEC/REST-API-wg/blob/5a8974308ef38e8ee4979e4a29b3b3a22c647822/json_repo/W/421.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82479/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_100_200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000509.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0583.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0590","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0590.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0358","title":"Digital Unix 4.0 MH inc 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Digital Unix 4.0 操作系统的 mh（消息处理）套件中的 inc 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地或远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的邮件消息触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而造成程序崩溃或执行任意代码，获取系统控制权限。该漏洞影响 Digital Unix 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0358"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.480","remediation":"立即从 Compaq（现 HP）获取并安装 Digital Unix 4.0 的安全补丁（补丁编号请查阅 CIAC 公告 J-027），或升级至 Tru64 UNIX 5.0 及以上版本。若无法立即打补丁，可移除 inc 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/inc）作为临时缓解措施，限制本地普通用户以 root 权限执行 inc 命令。建议改用 mailx 或 Mutt 替代 mh 套件处理本地邮件，降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-027.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12121"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0590.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0613","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0613.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0373","title":"Debian GNU/Linux Super 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 及多个类 Unix 系统中自带的 Super 工具存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。该程序以 setuid root 权限运行，用于授权普通用户以 root 身份执行特定命令。攻击者通过向 Super 提交超长的命令行参数触发缓冲区溢出，可覆盖返回地址并劫持控制流，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。由于攻击者需要本地系统访问权限，该漏洞影响范围局限于多用户环境，但一旦利用成功即实现完全提权。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0373"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.430","remediation":"升级 Debian GNU/Linux 上的 super 软件包至版本 3.12 及以上，该版本已修复缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，立即执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/super` 移除 suid 权限位以阻止提权利用，并考虑使用 sudo 替代 super 进行权限委派。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0373"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0613.toml"}]